Load Argo float meta

argo_meta_config_param(path, download = NULL, quiet = FALSE)

argo_meta_missions(path, download = NULL, quiet = FALSE)

argo_meta_trans_system(path, download = NULL, quiet = FALSE)

argo_meta_launch_config_param(path, download = NULL, quiet = FALSE)

argo_meta_sensor(path, download = NULL, quiet = FALSE)

argo_meta_param(path, download = NULL, quiet = FALSE)

argo_read_meta_config_param(file, vars = NULL)

argo_read_meta_missions(file, vars = NULL)

argo_read_meta_trans_system(file, vars = NULL)

argo_read_meta_launch_config_param(file, vars = NULL)

argo_read_meta_sensor(file, vars = NULL)

argo_read_meta_param(file, vars = NULL)

Arguments

path

A path relative to the root directory of argo_mirror().
download

A logical vector indicating whether or not a file should be downloaded. Defaults to the value of argo_should_download(), which is TRUE for files that do not exist in the cache.
quiet

Use FALSE to show which files are downloaded and for more verbose error messages.
file

A previously downloaded Argo NetCDF file.
vars

A vector of variable names to include. The ordering of the variables is not guaranteed, and variables that do not exist are ignored. For nc_read_*() and read_*() variants, these are the raw variable names (all caps, without "date" substituted for "juld").

Value

A tibble::tibble().

Examples

with_argo_example_cache({
  argo_meta_config_param("dac/csio/2900313/2900313_meta.nc")
})
